    <item>
      <title>中国股市暴跌：监管机构誓言稳定市场，但未提供细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-vows-to-stabilize-markets-offers-no-detail-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周五股价跌至五年低点后，中国证监会周日誓言要稳定市场，但政策制定者没有具体说明他们计划如何结束抛售。斯蒂芬·恩格尔在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-vows-to-stabilize-markets-offers-no-detail-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:04:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对“一带一路”沿线国家的投资创2018年以来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/chinese-investment-into-bri-nations-hits-highest-since-2018</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告称，去年中国对“一带一路”沿线国家的投资升至2018年以来的最高水平，企业向海外项目投入了近500亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/chinese-investment-into-bri-nations-hits-highest-since-2018</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券多头寄希望于鸽派的印度央行转向延长预算反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bond-bulls-pin-hopes-on-dovish-rbi-pivot-to-extend-budget-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度债券交易员预计，审慎的财政预算可能会促使央行发出鸽派货币政策倾斜的信号，并延续一年多来的最佳反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bond-bulls-pin-hopes-on-dovish-rbi-pivot-to-extend-budget-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗称中国需要产生更多经济活力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-needs-to-generate-more-economic-dynamism-citi-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗全球财富投资亚太区投资策略主管彭肯分享了他对中国股市和政府政策的看法。上周五股市在混乱的交易中跌至五年低点后，中国周日誓言要稳定市场，但政策制定者没有透露计划如何结束抛售的具体细节。彭在“彭博黎明：亚洲”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-needs-to-generate-more-economic-dynamism-citi-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 00:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将通过央行注资避开农历新年现金紧缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-set-to-skirt-lunar-new-year-cash-crunch-on-pboc-injection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国交易员可能会从他们的担忧中剔除迫在眉睫的现金紧缩，因为银行希望在即将到来的农历新年假期期间有充足的资金可以放贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-set-to-skirt-lunar-new-year-cash-crunch-on-pboc-injection</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 00:32:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国际货币基金组织救助结束，巴基斯坦的债券上涨面临选举考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/usd-pkr-pakistan-s-asia-beating-bond-rally-may-stall-as-elections-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者等待新领导人与国际货币基金组织达成融资协议以维持经济运转，巴基斯坦美元债券的涨势将在 1 月份成为亚洲表现最好的国家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/usd-pkr-pakistan-s-asia-beating-bond-rally-may-stall-as-elections-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 00:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔在“60分钟”节目中表示美联储对降息过早持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/powell-tells-60-minutes-fed-likely-to-wait-beyond-march-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者可能会等到 3 月份之后才降息，他试图向广大公众解释央行最终降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/powell-tells-60-minutes-fed-likely-to-wait-beyond-march-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 00:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国对胡塞武装的袭击加剧紧张局势，油价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国誓言对伊朗军队及其在中东的代理人进行更多打击，也门胡塞武装承诺对周末的轰炸进行报复，油价继去年 10 月以来最大单周跌幅后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:26:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔增加就业机会，国债延续跌势：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一早盘，由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔警告三月份降息的可能性，美国国债恢复抛售，加剧了周五强劲就业数据的影响。]]></description>
